e%20us%20and%20terms%20apply%20to%20offers%20listed%20(see%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Four-partners%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eadvertiser%20disclosure%20with%20our%20list%20of%20partners%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20more%20details).%20However%2C%20our%20opinions%20are%20our%20own.%20See%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fpersonal-finance-editorial-standards%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehow%20we%20rate%20products%20and%20services%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20help%20you%20make%20smart%20decisions%20with%20your%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227952%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman%20holding%20a%20paper%20bag%20of%20groceries%20uses%20her%20phone%20for%20a%20mobile%20payment%20processor%20at%20a%20farmers%20market.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67cb7cdd585f1dff88b1934d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223976%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECrypto%20credit%20cards%20offer%20rewards%20just%20like%20other%20rewards%20credit%20cards%20%E2%80%94%20but%20with%20cryptocurrency%20instead%20of%20points.%3Cp%3EFG%20Trade%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EIf%20you%20believe%20cryptocurrency%20will%20continue%20to%20rise%20in%20value%2C%20consider%20a%20crypto%20rewards%20credit%20card.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBefore%20jumping%20on%2C%20though%2C%20make%20sure%20you%20understand%20how%20volatile%20crypto%20markets%20are.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ELook%20into%20what%20types%20of%20spending%20are%20rewarded%20before%20committing%20to%20a%20rewards%20credit%20card.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAmericans%20love%20the%20cash%20back%2C%20travel%2C%20gift%20cards%2C%20and%20other%20rewards%20they%20can%20earn%20from%20swiping%20their%20credit%20cards.%20%3C%2Fspan%3EAccording%20to%20a%202024%20Morning%20Consult%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aba.com%2F-%2Fmedia%2Fdocuments%2Finfographics%2Fmorning-consult-consumer-policy-issues-survey-infographic.pdf%3Frev%3D7f713aa386bc4519b3b273260ac8313f%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esurvey%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20e%3Cspan%3Eight%20in%2010%20Americans%20have%20at%20least%20one%20credit%20card%20that%20offers%20rewards%2C%20and%2088%25%20say%20they%20value%20the%20reward%20programs%20their%20credit%20cards%20offer.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20you're%20a%20rewards%20lover%20%3Cem%3Eand%3C%2Fem%3E%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Fwhat-is-cryptocurrency%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ecryptocurrency%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20fan%2C%20there's%20a%20crop%20of%20cards%20that%20may%20hold%20extra%20appeal%20for%20you%3A%20crypto%20credit%20cards.%20These%20cards%20work%20similarly%20to%20other%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fcredit-cards%2Fbest-rewards-credit-cards%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Erewards%20credit%20cards%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20but%20instead%20of%20scoring%20common%20rewards%20like%20airplane%20miles%2C%20you'll%20earn%20cryptocurrencies%20such%20as%20bitcoin%20and%20ether.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20who%20believe%20in%20the%20future%20of%20crypto%20appreciate%20cards%20that%20let%20them%20earn%20and%20use%20digital%20currencies%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Brent%20Weiss%2C%20a%20certified%20financial%20planner%20and%20head%20of%20financial%20wellness%20at%20online%20financial%20planning%20firm%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Ffacet-wealth-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EFacet%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20Earning%20the%20rewards%20is%20akin%20to%20investing%2C%20since%20your%20rewards%20can%20grow%20in%20value%20if%20crypto%20prices%20increase.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20similar%20to%20receiving%20stock%20shares%20for%20spending%20on%20a%20traditional%20card%2C%26quot%3B%20Weiss%20adds.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20these%20rewards%20also%20come%20with%20risks.%20Here's%20what%20to%20know%20before%20opening%20a%20crypto%20credit%20card.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22273e815f-4d16-4dc6-92cc-a7fccf4eaab9%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20state%20of%20crypto%20credit%20cards%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELike%20crypto%20prices%2C%20the%20market%20for%20crypto%20credit%20cards%20has%20been%20volatile.%20When%20crypto%20was%20on%20a%20tear%20in%202021%2C%20several%20companies%20introduced%20these%20cards.%20But%20when%20bitcoin's%20price%20dropped%20from%20roughly%20%2464%2C000%20per%20coin%20to%20below%20%2420%2C000%20per%20coin%20in%20less%20than%20a%20year%20and%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fftx-sbf-crypto-saga-explained-what-happened-what-it-means-2022-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ecollapse%20of%20major%20crypto%20firm%20FTX%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20rattled%20the%20industry%2C%20those%20companies%20took%20note.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20example%2C%20digital%20asset%20lender%20BlockFi%20teamed%20up%20with%20Visa%20to%20launch%20a%20card%20that%20offered%201.5%25%20back%20in%20bitcoin%20with%20every%20purchase%20in%202021%2C%20only%20for%20BlockFi%20to%20go%20bankrupt%20in%202022.%20The%20Upgrade%20Bitcoin%20Rewards%20Visa%20Credit%20Card%20is%20another%20example%20of%20a%20crypto%20card%20that's%20no%20longer%20available.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMany%20in%20the%20industry%20are%20bullish%20on%20crypto%2C%20given%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcurrencies%2Fbitcoin-price-trump-national-strategic-reserve-debt-inflation-btc-crypto-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EPresident%20Donald%20Trump's%20friendly%20stance%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20toward%20digital%20assets.%20But%20for%20now%2C%20there%20are%20only%20two%20main%20options%20for%20people%20looking%20to%20earn%20crypto%20rewards%20with%20their%20credit%20card%20spending%3A%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Fgemini-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EGemini%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Credit%20Card%20and%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fcredit-cards%2Fvenmo-credit-card-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EVenmo%20Credit%20Card%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Gemini%20card%20allows%20you%20to%20earn%20up%20to%204%25%20back%20(the%20exact%20amount%20depends%20on%20the%20spending%20type)%20in%20bitcoin%2C%20ether%2C%20or%20more%20than%2050%20other%20cryptocurrencies.%20The%20Venmo%20card%20lets%20you%20sign%20up%20for%20a%20feature%20that%20will%20automatically%20use%20your%20earned%20cash%20back%20to%20purchase%20bitcoin%2C%20bitcoin%20cash%2C%20ether%2C%20litecoin%2C%20or%20PayPal's%20stablecoin.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f8b1e4ed-6145-48d7-8d2a-949378196f45%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EHow%20crypto%20credit%20cards%20work%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECrypto%20credit%20cards%20have%20similar%20transaction%20processes%2C%20provider%20networks%20and%20usabilities%20to%20traditional%20credit%20cards%2C%20Weiss%20explains.%20You%20can%20use%20them%20like%20a%20regular%20credit%20card%20at%20any%20merchant%20that%20accepts%20the%20network%20(most%20run%20on%20Visa%20or%20Mastercard)%2C%20and%20your%20purchases%20go%20through%20instantly.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20while%20traditional%20credit%20cards%20might%20offer%20points%20or%20miles%20redeemable%20for%20travel%2C%20gift%20cards%2C%20or%20statement%20credits%2C%20crypto%20cards%20let%20you%20accumulate%20crypto%2C%20which%20can%20be%20held%2C%20traded%2C%20or%20converted%20to%20cash.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a51cf054-c1fe-4a63-9571-1fdad7ba903a%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EPros%20and%20cons%20of%20crypto%20credit%20cards%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECrypto%20credit%20cards%20come%20with%20pros%20such%20as%20growth%20potential%20%E2%80%94%20since%20the%20value%20of%20your%20crypto%20can%20grow%20faster%20than%20traditional%20cash%20back%20or%20points%20when%20crypto%20prices%20jump%20%E2%80%94%20as%20well%20as%20supporting%20crypto%20innovation%20and%20adoption.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20they%20come%20with%20downsides%2C%20too%2C%20including%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finvestments-safer-than-crypto-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehigher%20volatility%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20If%20you%20earn%201%25%20back%20in%20bitcoin%20and%20bitcoin's%20price%20drops%2050%25%20overnight%2C%20your%20rewards%20lose%20half%20their%20value%20instantly%2C%20says%20Ben%20Loughery%2C%20a%20certified%20financial%20planner%20and%20founder%20of%20Lock%20Wealth%20Management.%20Crypto%20also%20comes%20with%20regulatory%20uncertainty.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BSome%20banks%20are%20still%20hesitating%20to%20fully%20embrace%20crypto%20because%20of%20government%20regulations%2C%26quot%3B%20Loughery%20says.%20Regulatory%20changes%20could%20impact%20your%20card%20or%20how%20rewards%20are%20taxed%20in%20the%20future.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere's%20also%20limited%20flexibility%20and%20an%20opportunity%20cost%20for%20crypto%20as%20a%20reward%20versus%20more%20traditional%20rewards%20like%20travel%2C%20gift%20cards%20and%20cash%20back.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BRewards%20are%20often%20locked%20into%20crypto%2C%26quot%3B%20Weiss%20says.%20%26quot%3BYou%20may%20lose%20out%20on%20the%20flexible%20redemption%20options.%26quot%3B%20He%20adds%20that%20in%20some%20cases%2C%20other%20rewards%20cards%20might%20offer%20better%20overall%20returns%20(like%20cash%20back%20or%20travel%20points)%20for%20how%20you%20spend.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThen%2C%20there's%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Ftaxes%2Fhow-to-report-crypto-on-taxes%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Etax%20component%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20You'll%20likely%20owe%20capital%20gains%20taxes%20when%20you%20sell%20or%20convert%20crypto%20%E2%80%94%20a%20consideration%20you%20don't%20have%20to%20worry%20about%20with%20traditional%20rewards.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d6c2800b-e0b7-4b3b-ab14-5a3976014492%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20to%20consider%20before%20opening%20a%20crypto%20credit%20card%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20choosing%20a%20credit%20card%20of%20any%20kind%2C%20Weiss%20says%20to%20consider%20how%20you%20spend%20your%20money%20since%20different%20cards%20reward%20different%20types%20of%20purchases%20at%20varying%20rates%2C%20as%20well%20as%20how%20each%20card%20rewards%20you%20for%20spending.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYou%20want%20a%20card%20that%20provides%20better%20rewards%20for%20what%20you%20actually%20spend%20money%20on%2C%20whether%20that%20be%20gas%2C%20groceries%2C%20meals%20out%20at%20restaurants%2C%20or%20something%20else.%20You%20also%20need%20to%20understand%20how%20you%20can%20redeem%20your%20rewards%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20fees%20and%20rates.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20a%20crypto%20credit%20card%20comes%20with%20the%20need%20for%20extra%20considerations.%20In%20addition%20to%20keeping%20up%20with%20a%20regulatory%20environment%20that's%20in%20flux%2C%20you%20also%20want%20to%20take%20security%20precautions.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BMake%20sure%20your%20crypto%20rewards%20