%E2%80%94%20a%20task%20military%20and%20conflict%20analysts%20told%20BI%20involves%20huge%20challenges.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22musk%20trump%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67abc139eb4be2fff9a452ae%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22684%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPresident%20Donald%20Trump%20and%20Elon%20Musk%20in%20the%20Oval%20Office.%3Cp%3E(Photo%2FAlex%20Brandon)%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22802c0c2d-0999-4aa9-b3e2-61905242ee47%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EStarlink%20provides%20Ukraine%20with%20a%20lifeline%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20Russia%20launched%20its%20full-scale%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine%20in%20February%202022%2C%20Ukraine%20has%20depended%20on%20Starlink%20to%20keep%20both%20its%20military%20and%20civilian%20broadband%20services%20running.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20June%202022%2C%20Musk%20said%20SpaceX%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-spacex-sent-starlink-satellite-internet-terminals-ukraine-2022-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edelivered%2015%2C000%20Starlink%20terminals%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStarlink%20was%20initially%20provided%20to%20Ukraine%20by%20SpaceX%20free%20of%20charge%2C%20and%20then%20was%20paid%20for%20by%20the%20US%20government.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.politico.eu%2Farticle%2Feu-to-help-ukraine-replace-musks-starlink%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENow%2C%20Poland%20foots%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20bill%20for%20around%20half%20of%20Ukraine's%2040%2C000%20terminals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20as%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20and%20his%20allies%20continue%20to%20put%20pressure%20on%20Ukraine%20to%20reach%20a%20cease-fire%20deal%20with%20Russia%2C%20European%20countries%20are%20urgently%20looking%20for%20contingency%20plans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20SpaceX%20proves%20to%20be%20an%20unreliable%20provider%20we%20will%20be%20forced%20to%20look%20for%20other%20suppliers%2C%26quot%3B%20Sikorski%20told%20Musk%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmong%20those%20that%20could%20fill%20the%20gap%20are%20France's%20Eutelsat%2C%20a%20major%20rival%20to%20Starlink%2C%20and%20the%20European%20Union's%20GovSatCom%20initiative.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEutelsat's%20stock%20price%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstarlink-competitor-eutelsat-oneweb-trump-us-aid-ukraine-internet-satellite-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eskyrocketed%20in%20recent%20weeks%2C%20as%20BI%20previously%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20the%20company's%20CEO%2C%20Eva%20Berneke%2C%20told%20Bloomberg%20that%20it%20was%20looking%20into%20the%20viability%20of%20replacing%20large%20numbers%20of%20satellite%20broadband%20terminals%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20saying%20it%20would%20need%20%26quot%3Ba%20couple%20of%20months%26quot%3B%20to%20replace%20the%2040%2C000%20Starlink%20terminals%20deployed%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFour%20European%20satellite%20operators%20also%20told%20the%20Financial%20Times%20last%20week%20that%20they%20were%20in%20talks%20with%20European%20governments%20and%20EU%20institutions%20over%20how%20to%20provide%20backup%20connectivity%20for%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Miguel%20%C3%81ngel%20Garc%C3%ADa%20Primo%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20Hisdesat%2C%20one%20of%20the%20companies%2C%20told%20the%20outlet%20that%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Bvery%20difficult%20if%20not%20impossible%20for%20someone%20to%20deploy%20the%20same%20number%20of%20terminals%20Starlink%20already%20has%20because%20they%20have%20been%20accumulated%20over%20years.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225794%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20rocket%20carrying%20a%20Eutelsat%20satellite%20lifts%20off%20from%20its%20launchpad.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67c7d49069253ccddf984b4d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223865%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20Eutelsat%20satellite%20launched%20in%202022.%20The%20company%20has%20seen%20its%20share%20price%20jump%20in%20recent%20weeks.%3Cp%3EJODY%20AMIET%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2252aa033c-e0f8-4091-99e7-c4525c0e22c6%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMajor%20obstacles%20ahead%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20their%20public%20spat%20on%20Sunday%2C%20Musk%20mocked%20Sikorski%20over%20his%20suggestion%20that%20Poland%20could%20find%20a%20Starlink%20replacement%2C%20saying%20there%20was%20%26quot%3Bno%20substitute%26quot%3B%20for%20his%20network.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EClayton%20Swope%2C%20a%20senior%20fellow%20in%20the%20Defense%20and%20Security%20Department%20at%20the%20Center%20for%20Strategic%20and%20International%20Studies%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20replacing%20Starlink%20would%20present%20serious%20challenges.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BStarlink%20has%20provided%20Ukraine%20an%20indispensable%20edge%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20describing%20it%20as%20%26quot%3Bthe%20world's%20low-latency%2C%20high-speed%20satellite%20broadband%20service%20par%20excellence.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReplacing%20it%20%26quot%3Bwould%20be%20a%20huge%20complication%20for%20Ukraine%20at%20a%20time%20when%20it%20already%20has%20a%20bunch%20of%20other%20thorny%20problems%20to%20worry%20about%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20referring%2C%20among%20other%20issues%2C%20to%20Trump's%20decision%20to%20stop%20US%20military%20aid%20and%20intelligence%20sharing%20with%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20Maxar%20Technologies%2C%20a%20commercial%20satellite%20imaging%20company%2C%20said%20that%20it%20was%20suspending%20the%20sharing%20of%20US%20government-commissioned%20imagery%20with%20Ukraine%2C%20following%20government%20directives%2C%20a%20move%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcutting-satellite-imagery-weakens-ukraines-defenses-lawmaker-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eseverely%20constrains%20Ukrainian%20drone%20pilots%20trying%20to%20defend%20their%20homeland%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Ukrainian%20drone%20operator%20previously%20told%20BI%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmaxar-pulling-satellite-imagery-will-hurt-ukraines-drone-abilities-pilot-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMaxar's%20images%20have%20been%20essential%20to%20flying%20in%20GPS-jammed%20areas%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20raising%20concerns%20for%20future%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cd7d3731-adea-4b30-99a9-ccfee217eb4c%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMusk-Ukraine%20rift%20a%20'wake-up%20call'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMelanie%20Garson%2C%20an%20associate%20professor%20in%20International%20Conflict%20Resolution%20%26amp%3B%20International%20Security%20at%20University%20College%20London%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20if%20Starlink%20was%20no%20longer%20available%2C%20it%20would%20have%20cascading%20effects%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20with%20military%20and%20civilians%20losing%20internet%20access.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkrainian%20weaponry%20dependent%20on%20Starlink%20data%20wouldn't%20be%20able%20to%20function%2C%20she%20said%2C%20while%20Ukrainian%20troops%20would%20likely%20have%20to%20resort%20to%20communicating%20by%20radio%2C%20an%20approach%20that's%20susceptible%20to%20electronic%20jamming.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGarson%20also%20said%20that%20alternative%20satellite%20broadband%20systems%20aren't%20as%20user-friendly%20as%20Starlink%20and%20don't%20have%20the%20same%20capacity%2C%20so%20connectivity%20could%20be%20less%20dependable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20challenge%20is%20that%20Starlink%20has%20over%207%2C000%20satellites%2C%20meaning%20its%20network%20can%20offer%20strong%20coverage%20all%20around%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThree%20major%20European%20aerospace%20companies%20%E2%80%94%20Airbus%2C%20Leonardo%2C%20and%20Thales%20Alenia%20Space%20%E2%80%94%20are%20exploring%20a%20partnership%20to%20compete%20against%20SpaceX%20in%20the%20satellite%20industry.%20An%20Airbus%20spokesperson%20told%20BI%20that%20the%20companies%20had%20begun%20%26quot%3Bpreliminary%20and%20non-binding%26quot%3B%20discussions%20to%20strengthen%20Europe's%20position%20in%20the%20global%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGarson%20told%20BI%20the%20situation%20could%20also%20stimulate%20Ukrainian%20resolve%2C%20with%20Ukraine's%20Starlink%20network%20%26quot%3Bhard%2C%20although%20not%20impossible%20to%20replace%20under%20pressure.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReplacing%20the%20system%20%26quot%3Bwill%20not%20be%20fatal%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20but%20it%20%26quot%3Bwill%20create%20a%20significant%20slowdown%2C%20as%20well%20as%20have%20a%20psychological%20impact.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBeyond%20the%20battlefield%2C%26quot%3B%20Garson%20added%2C%20%26quot%3Bthis%20needs%20to%20be%20a%20wake-up%20call%20for%20countries%20on%20outsourcing%20communications%20resilience%20into%20private%20companies.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmusk-starlink-threats-europe-faces-obstacles-replace-eutelsat-ukraine-trump-2025-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741690626000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67c7d49069253ccddf984b4d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmusk-starlink-threats-europe-faces-obstacles-replace-eutelsat-ukraine-trump-2025-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Europe%20is%20looking%20at%20options%20to%20replace%20Starlink%20in%20Ukraine%20if%20Elon%20Musk%20pulls%20access%20%E2%80%94%20but%20the%20scale%20of%20the%20task%20is%20daunting.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22tporter%40businessinsider.com%20(Tom%20Porter%2CThibault%20Spirlet)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmusk-starlink-threats-europe-faces-obstacles-replace-eutelsat-ukraine-trump-2025-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22tit