0animation%20and%20audiobooks%2C%20where%20fight%20scenes%20and%20all%20these%20effects%20can%20be%20taxing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20days%2C%20I%20just%20leave%20the%20booth%20crying%20because%20some%20scenes%20are%20emotionally%20hard%20to%20record.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b4adb897-0c4e-48ae-a54c-c3346ce39989%5C%22%3EMoney%20doesn't%20have%20to%20be%20a%20barrier%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20first%20started%20voice%20acting%2C%20I%20was%20a%20recent%20college%20grad%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20a%20pandemic.%20I%20didn't%20have%20any%20money%2C%20and%20the%20biggest%20thing%20I%20saw%20when%20looking%20into%20how%20to%20get%20into%20voice%20acting%20was%20that%20I%20had%20to%20invest%20all%20of%20this%20money%20in%20myself%20to%20do%20this%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20would%20have%20to%20spend%20money%20on%20a%20booth%2C%20a%20fancy%20microphone%2C%20a%20reel%2C%20marketing%20materials%2C%20new%20headshots%2C%20and%20everything%20else.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20very%20easy%20to%20let%20money%20be%20a%20barrier%2C%20but%20it%20shouldn't%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman%20holds%20a%20book%20outside%20of%20a%20bookstore.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67af716feb4be2fff9a4b348%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKhaya%20Fraites%20is%20a%20voice%20actor.%3Cp%3EKhaya%20Fraites%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EPut%20your%20reel%20together%20yourself%20and%20get%20your%20friends%20to%20listen%20to%20it%20and%20give%20you%20feedback.%20Submit%20to%20projects%20online.%20Just%20put%20yourself%20out%20there%20because%20I%20think%20that's%20what's%20holding%20people%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20publishers%20host%20free%20annual%20seminars%20or%20classes%2C%20and%20that's%20how%20I%20got%20into%20working%20at%20Penguin%20Random%20House%20and%20Macmillan.%20They%20both%20had%20free%20Zoom%20seminars%2C%20where%20I%20was%20able%20to%20audition%20for%20producers%20and%20make%20an%20introduction.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EConnect%20with%20other%20voice%20actors%2C%20and%20don't%20be%20afraid%20to%20ask%20questions.%20I%20have%20a%20friend%20who%20was%20narrating%20when%20I%20first%20started%2C%20and%20I%20asked%20her%20a%20million%20questions%20during%20the%20pandemic%2C%20just%20trying%20to%20figure%20out%20everything%20and%20how%20to%20get%20started.%20Don't%20be%20afraid%20to%20reach%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvoice-actor-narrating-audiobooks-fourth-wing-onyx-storm-2025-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741689661000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67af62e37bb3f854015cecac%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvoice-actor-narrating-audiobooks-fourth-wing-onyx-storm-2025-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Khaya%20Fraites%20has%20been%20a%20voice%20actor%20for%20five%20years.%20She%20stars%20as%20Violet%20Sorrengail%20in%20GraphicAudio's%20adaptations%20of%20the%20%26quot%3BFourth%20Wing%26quot%3B%20series.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22sgrindell%40businessinsider.com%20(Samantha%20Grindell)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvoice-actor-narrating-audiobooks-fourth-wing-onyx-storm-2025-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20What%20'Power-Dressers'%20-%20And%20Trump%20-%20Can%20Learn%20From%20Gandhi%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOne%20would%20have%20thought%20that%20Mohandas%20Karamchand%20Gandhi%20settled%20this%20debate%20long%20ago.%20That%20real%20power%20dressing%20lies%20in%20how%20powerfully%20your%20dress%20transmits%20who%20you%20are%20and%20what%20you%20stand%20for%E2%80%94and%20not%20in%20donning%20a%20so-called%20appropriate%20set%20of%20clothes.%20Or%2C%20indeed%2C%20a%20sharp%20suit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201931%2C%20Gandhi%20went%20to%20meet%20King%20George%20V%20at%20Buckingham%20Palace%2C%20dressed%20in%20his%20usual%20handspun%20short%20dhoti%20and%20shawl.%20While%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20guests%20were%20arrayed%20in%20splendorous%20morning%20coats%E2%80%94as%20the%20dress%20code%20had%20called%20for%20that%20day%E2%80%94Gandhi%20saw%20no%20reason%20to%20shed%20the%20attire%20that%20he%20had%20embraced%20in%20Madurai%20on%20September%2022%2C%201921%2C%20to%20express%20his%20oneness%20with%20the%20poor%20people%20of%20colonised%20India.%20Some%20royal%20eyebrows%20may%20have%20been%20infinitesimally%20raised%2C%20some%20stiff%20upper%20lips%20may%20have%20quivered%2C%20but%20at%20the%20tea%20party%2C%20at%20least%2C%20the%20Mahatma%20was%20not%20questioned%20about%20his%20sartorial%20preference.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20a%20journalist%20later%20asked%20him%20if%20he%20wasn't%20somewhat%20underdressed%20for%20the%20occasion%2C%20Gandhi%20famously%20retorted%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20king%20had%20enough%20on%20for%20both%20of%20us%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EBullying%20Zelensky%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20week%20another%20journalist%20posed%20a%20similar%20question%20to%20Ukraine%20President%20Volodymyr%20Zelensky%2C%20who%20has%20given%20up%20decorous%20formal%20wear%20since%20Russia%20invaded%20his%20country%20three%20years%20ago%2C%20and%20has%20worn%20dark%20sweatshirts%20or%20sweaters%20and%20combat%20boots%20to%20express%20his%20solidarity%20with%20his%20people%20who%20are%20fighting%20a%20war.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhy%20don't%20you%20wear%20a%20suit%3F%E2%80%9D%20asked%20Brian%20Glenn%2C%20a%20correspondent%20for%20the%20right-wing%20television%20channel%2C%20%3Cem%3EReal%20American%20Voice%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20when%20Zelensky%20was%20meeting%20with%20US%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20at%20the%20White%20House%20Oval%20Office.%20%E2%80%9CYou're%20at%20the%20highest%20level%20in%20this%20country's%20office%2C%20and%20you%20refuse%20to%20wear%20a%20suit.%E2%80%9D%20Glenn%20said%2C%20drawing%20titters%20from%20many%20of%20his%20fellow%20journalists%20and%20a%20wide%20smirk%20from%20Vice-President%20JD%20Vance.%20%E2%80%9CDo%20you%20own%20a%20suit%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20went%20on%20to%20demand%20boorishly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIncidentally%2C%20it%20was%20Trump%20himself%20who%20had%20set%20up%20the%20cue%20for%20this%20obnoxious%20line%20of%20questioning.%20Receiving%20Zelensky%20on%20the%20steps%20of%20the%20White%20House%2C%20Trump%20gestured%20to%20him%20and%20said%2C%20with%20obvious%20snark%2C%20%E2%80%9CHe%20is%20all%20dressed%20up%20today.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EFashion%20Is%20Politics%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20doubt%2C%20both%20Trump%20and%20his%20chosen%20brood%20of%20reporters%20are%20aware%20that%20Zelensky%20has%20been%20similarly%20dressed%20at%20every%20public%20appearance%2C%20television%20interview%2C%20meeting%20with%20world%20leaders%2C%20and%2C%20so%20on%2C%20since%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20war%20in%202022.%20And%20by%20doing%20so%2C%20he%20sends%20a%20powerful%20message%20%E2%80%94%20that%20he%20stands%20with%20his%20people%2C%20a%20people%20fighting%20for%20survival%20and%20living%20under%20the%20constant%20threat%20of%20being%20bombed%2C%20maimed%20or%20killed%20by%20Russian%20aggression.%20This%20is%20no%20time%20for%20him%20to%20go%20swanning%20around%20in%20style%2C%20he%20seems%20to%20be%20saying%E2%80%94this%20is%20a%20time%20to%20hunker%20down%20and%20beat%20back%20the%20enemy%20at%20the%20door.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20this%20is%20well%20known.%20Hence%2C%20that%20Zelensky's%20choice%20of%20dress%20raised%20some%20MAGA%20hackles%20has%20less%20to%20do%20with%20a%20perceived%20lack%20of%20respect%20for%20the%20Oval%20Office%20and%20more%20to%20do%20with%20a%20blast%20of%20antagonism%20towards%20the%20political%20message%20that%20it%20conveys.%20After%20all%2C%20as%20the%20internet%20hasn't%20stopped%20pointing%20out%20since%20the%20incident%2C%20Elon%20Musk%2C%20Trump's%20billionaire%20benefactor%20and%20slasher-in-chief%20of%20government%20jobs%2C%20has%20often%20come%20to%20the%20Oval%20Office%20dressed%20in%20informal%20sweatshirts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhen%20Your%20Clothes%20Speak%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne's%20body%20and%20the%20way%20one%20chooses%20to%20dress%20it%20(or%20not)%20can%20make%20charged%20political%20statements.%20Gandhi%2C%20the%20messianic%E2%80%94and%20some%20would%20say%2C%20wily%E2%80%94mass%20leader%20that%20he%20was%2C%20understood%20this%20when%20he%20adopted%20the%20austere%20loincloth%20as%20his%20forever%20uniform.%20Women%20and%20girls%20in%20non-Islamic%20countries%20who%20choose%20to%20wear%20the%20burqa%20or%20the%20hijab%20are%20also%20making%20a%20political%20statement%E2%80%94that%20they%20have%20a%20right%20to%20express%20their%20religious%20and%20cultural%20identity%2C%20in%20spite%20of%20the%20feminist%20insistence%20that%20such%20attire%20is%20regressive%20and%20anti-women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20thousands%20of%20Americans%20marched%20wearing%20T-shirts%20emblazoned%20with%20the%20legend%20'BlackLivesMatter'%20after%20a%20white%20policeman%20charged%20with%20shooting%20a%20black%20teenager%20in%202013%20was%20let%20off%2C%20it%20was%20a%20resounding%20political%20statement%20against%20racial%20discrimination.%20When%20a%20group%20of%20women%20in%20Paris%20went%20topless%20to%20protest%20against%20gender%20violence%20in%20November%202024%2C%20holding%20placards%20saying%20%E2%80%9CFemme%2C%20Vie%2C%20Libert%C3%A9%E2%80%9D%20(Women%2C%20Life%2C%20Liberty)%2C%20it%20was%20a%20political%20fashion%20statement%20that%20was%20as%20in-your-face%20as%20it%20could%20get.%20And%20last%20week%2C%20when%20women%20leaders%20of%20the%20Democratic%20Party%20came%20dressed%20in%20pink%20to%20listen%20to%20Trump's%20speech%20to%20Congress%2C%20that%20too%20was%20a%20political%20statement%2C%20albeit%20a%20somewhat%20feeble%20one.%20They%20wore%20pink%2C%20they%20said%2C%20to%20protest%20against%20the%20President's%20policies%20which%20were%20harming%20women%20and%20families.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20'Unsuited'%20Leaders%20Put%20Us%20Off%20So%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20thing%20about%20making%20your%20fashion%20speak%20your%20politics%20is%20that%20those%20who%20stand%20on%20the%20other%20side%20of%20that%20politics%20will%20look%20upon%20your%20fashion%20choice%20with%20hostility%20and%20derision.%20Winston%20Churchill%2C%20the%20imperialist%20British%20leader%2C%20referred%20to%20Gandhi%20as%20someone%20%E2%80%9Cposing%20as%20a%20half-naked%20fakir%E2%80%9D.%20And%20many%20governments%20around%20the%20world%20have%20banned%20the%20burqa%2C%20while%20regulating%20the%20use%20of%20the%20hijab%2C%20arguing%20that%20they%20militate%20against%20the%20democratic%20values%20of%20equality%20and%20women's%20rights%2C%20and%20ignoring%20the%20question%20as%20to%20whether%20the%20state%20had%20any%20right%20at%20all%20to%20legislate%20on%20how%20women%20choose%20to%20dress%20themselves.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20could%20be%20that%20a%20Trump%20administration%20starting%20to%20betray%20an%20incipient%20tilt%20towards%20Russia%20found%20Zelensky's%20sartorial%20choice%20offensive%20for%20precisely%20that%20reason.%20The%20Ukraine%20President's%20humble%20attire%2C%20his%20boots%20and%20his%20chunky%20black%20or%20military%20green%20sweaters%2C%20serves%20as%20a%20constant%20reminder%20that%20his%20country%20is%20at%20war%2C%20and%20Russia%20is%20the%20aggressor%20in%20this%20bloody%20conflict.%20Perhaps%20it%20seemed%20disrespectful%20to%20Trump%20and%20his%20proxies%20because%20their%20respect%20for%2C%20and%20sense%20of%20solidarity%20with%2C%20the%20plight%20of%20the%20people%20whom%20he%20represents%20was%20dwindling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20are%20readying%20to%20abandon%20a%20friend%2C%20you%20don't%20want%20to%20be%20reminded%20of%20his%20predicament