ficient%2C%20sending%20its%20stock%20soaring.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20Chinese%20AI%20models%20gaining%20ground%20fast%2C%20here%20are%20four%20key%20players%20to%20watch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22bf606924-41cf-495d-bc35-a10a114d1153%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20DeepSeek's%20R1%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDeepSeek%20was%20the%20first%20Chinese%20AI%20startup%20to%20shake%20up%20the%20industry.%20In%20January%2C%20its%20new%20model%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fdeepseek-ai-tech-stocks-selloff-chatgpt-china-artificial-intelligence-chips-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esent%20some%20US%20tech%20stocks%20plunging%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20raised%20questions%20about%20whether%20the%20US%20lead%20in%20AI%20has%20slipped.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20startup%2C%20based%20in%20Hang%20Zhou%2C%20was%20founded%20in%202023%20by%20hedge%20fund%20entrepreneur%20Liang%20Wenfeng.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20buying%20thousands%20of%20Nvidia%20chips%2C%20Wenfeng%20built%20DeepSeek's%20R1%20reasoning%20model%20on%20its%20V3%20base%20model%2C%20training%20it%20on%20around%202%2C000%20Nvidia%20H800%20chips%20at%20an%20overall%20cost%20of%20roughly%20%245.6%20million%2C%20the%20startup%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20a%20fraction%20of%20what%20top%20players%20like%20Meta%20and%20OpenAI%20are%20spending.%20Mark%20Zuckerberg%20has%20said%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmark-zuckerberg-meta-ai-investment-capital-expenditure-datacenter-deepseek-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMeta%20plans%20to%20spend%20over%20%2460%20billion%20this%20year%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20it%20doubles%20down%20on%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20its%20lower%20cost%2C%20its%20R1%20model%20rivals%20top%20competitors%20like%20ChatGPT's%20o1%2C%20DeepSeek%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIts%20impact%20on%20the%20AI%20chip%20market%20was%20immediate%3A%20Nvidia's%20stock%20plunged%20nearly%2017%25%2C%20wiping%20hundreds%20of%20billions%20from%20its%20market%20cap.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMicrosoft%20CEO's%2C%20Satya%20Nadella%2C%20wrote%20on%20X%20in%20January%3A%20%26quot%3BJevons%20paradox%20strikes%20again!%26quot%3B%E2%80%94%20suggesting%20that%20as%20AI%20becomes%20more%20efficient%20and%20accessible%2C%20demand%20will%20only%20skyrocket.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMarc%20Andreessen%2C%20the%20cofounder%20of%20storied%20Silicon%20Valley%20venture%20capital%20firm%20Andreessen%20Horowitz%2C%20took%20it%20a%20step%20further.%20He%20called%20DeepSeek's%20R1%20%26quot%3BAI's%20Sputnik%20moment%2C%26quot%3B%20likening%20it%20to%20the%20Soviet%20satellite%20launch%20that%20triggered%20the%20space%20race.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20DeepSeek's%20R1%20has%20its%20limits.%20While%20it%20appears%20capable%20of%20doing%20much%20of%20what%20ChatGPT%20can%2C%20it%20couches%20answers%20related%20to%20sensitive%20issues%20in%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a1abad75-b3cc-4184-8b8c-621999581616%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Alibaba's%20QwQ-32B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAlibaba%20has%20become%20a%20key%20player%20to%20watch%20after%20it%20open-sourced%20its%20QwQ-32B%20model%20last%20week.%20The%20company%20said%20the%20model%20used%20less%20data%20than%20DeepSeek.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20move%20sent%20Alibaba's%20stock%20surging%208%25%20over%20two%20days%2C%20while%20Nvidia%20took%20another%20hit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlibaba%20said%20its%20QwQ-32B%20model%2C%20with%20one-fifth%20of%20the%20parameters%20of%20DeepSeek-R1%2C%20is%20designed%20for%20efficiency.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20model%20is%20now%20open-source%20on%20platforms%20including%20Hugging%20Face.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman-openai-ai-approaches-deepseek-meta-open-source-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOpen-source%20models%3C%2Fa%3E%20allow%20for%20the%20free%20and%20open%20sharing%20of%20software%20to%20anyone%20for%20any%20purpose.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlibaba's%20shares%20in%20Hong%20Kong%20and%20its%20secondary%20listing%20in%20New%20York%20are%20up%20nearly%2070%25%20so%20far%20this%20year%2C%20though%20its%20%24348.8%20billion%20market%20cap%20is%20still%20much%20smaller%20than%20Amazon's%20%242.05%20trillion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20has%20been%20on%20a%20hot%20streak.%20Last%20month%2C%20its%20stock%20surged%20after%20a%20partnership%20with%20Apple%20to%20bring%20AI%20features%20to%20iPhones%20in%20China.%20Shares%20also%20climbed%20on%20news%20of%20Xi%20Jinping%20meeting%20with%20the%20country's%20tech%20moguls%2C%20including%20from%20Alibaba.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarly%20this%20month%2C%20the%20company%20announced%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Falibaba-share-price-china-ecommerce-ai-agi-tech-markets-deepseek-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eplans%20to%20invest%20at%20least%20380%20billion%20Chinese%20yuan%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20%2453%20billion%2C%20in%20cloud%20computing%20and%20AI%20infrastructure%20over%20the%20next%20three%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a2a373ea-930d-4b87-b404-af9703157818%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20Tencent's%20Yuanbao%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETencent's%20AI%20chatbot%20Yuanbao%20topped%20China's%20iOS%20App%20Store%20last%20week%2C%20surpassing%20DeepSeek%20as%20the%20most%20downloaded%20free%20app%2C%20Bloomberg%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETencent%2C%20based%20in%20Shenzhen%2C%20operates%20China's%20biggest%20social%20media%20app%20WeChat%20%E2%80%94%20which%20is%20used%20by%20nearly%201.4%20billion%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20the%20company%20added%20a%20download%20button%20for%20Yuanbao%20in%20WeChat%2C%20making%20the%20AI%20chatbot%20more%20accessible%20to%20the%20app's%20users%2C%20the%20South%20China%20Morning%20Post%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYuanbao%20is%20now%20the%20third%20most%20downloaded%20free%20app%20in%20China's%20iOS%20App%20Store%2C%20leading%20behind%20DeepSeek%20and%20ByteDance's%20Doubao.%20Doubao%20is%20a%20ChatGPT-like%20conversational%20bot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20February%2C%20Tencent%20integrated%20DeepSeek's%20R1%20into%20several%20of%20its%20products%2C%20including%20WeChat's%20search%20feature%20and%20a%20virtual%20companion%20in%20its%20evergreen%20game%20Peacekeepr%20Elite%2C%20Bloomberg%20reported%20last%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20added%20that%20Tencent%20also%20launched%20a%20Hunyuan%20Turbo%20edition%20that%20it%20says%20delivers%20answers%20faster%20than%20DeepSeek.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETencent's%20shares%20surged%2010%25%20over%20two%20days%20last%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2284fb3b72-938f-4608-9f04-c2940b13d796%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E4.%20Manus%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmanus-ai-china-agent-hype-deepseek-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EManus%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20just%20become%20China's%20latest%20AI%20sensation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20multiple%20reports%2C%20it%20was%20built%20by%20Chinese%20startup%20Monica%2C%20which%20appears%20to%20be%20a%20subsidiary%20of%20The%20Butterfly%20Effect.%20Manus'%20privacy%20policy%20said%20that%20The%20Butterfly%20Effect%20is%20a%20Singapore-registered%20entity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EResearchers%20at%20Monica%20said%20Manus%20is%20the%20world's%20first%20fully%20autonomous%20AI%20agent.%20Unlike%20chatbots%20that%20require%20multiple%20inputs%2C%20it%20can%20complete%20complex%20tasks%20like%20sorting%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9s%2C%20analyzing%20stocks%2C%20scraping%20data%2C%20and%20even%20building%20websites%20after%20a%20single%20prompt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Manus'%20website%2C%20it%20outperforms%20OpenAI's%20Deep%20Research%20model%20on%20the%20GAIA%20benchmark%2C%20a%20tool%20for%20comparing%20models.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFollowing%20its%20debut%20last%20week%2C%20some%20users%20questioned%20whether%20Manus%20was%20built%20from%20scratch%2C%20suggesting%20it%20might%20be%20more%20of%20an%20AI%20wrapper%20leveraging%20other%20models%2C%20like%20Anthropic's%20Cl