tching%20170%20kilometres%20across%20the%20desert%2C%20housed%20within%20two%20parallel%20skyscrapers%20taller%20than%20the%20Empire%20State%20Building.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20scale%20has%20proved%20overwhelming.%20The%20original%20plan%20to%20build%2016%20km%20of%20The%20Line%20by%202030%20was%20already%20ambitious%2C%20requiring%20more%20glass%20and%20steel%20than%20exists%20in%20entire%20cities.%20Even%20that%20was%20later%20revised%20down%20to%202.4%20km%2C%20with%20only%20a%20half-mile%20section%2C%20including%20a%20stadium%20-%20expected%20by%202034.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEngineering%20challenges%20and%20rising%20costs%20have%20forced%20compromises.%20The%20Line's%201%2C640-foot%20height%20makes%20construction%20difficult%2C%20and%20Neom%20officials%20suggested%20lowering%20it%20to%201%2C000%20feet%20to%20cut%20costs.%20The%20Crown%20Prince%20rejected%20this%2C%20insisting%20on%20finding%20savings%20elsewhere.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-07%2Fqu045a2g_saudi-arabia-mirror-city-afp_625x300_27_July_22.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ski%20resort%2C%20Trojena%2C%20has%20also%20seen%20costs%20spiral.%20The%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%2C%20citing%20a%202023%20review%2C%20found%20a%20%2410%20billion%20surge%20in%20expenses.%20To%20balance%20the%20books%2C%20revenue%20projections%20were%20reportedly%20inflated%20-%20hotel%20room%20rates%20were%20suddenly%20tripled%20or%20quadrupled%20to%20justify%20the%20investment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaudi%20officials%20have%20long%20insisted%20that%20Neom%20will%20eventually%20attract%20private%20investment.%20But%20foreign%20direct%20investment%20in%20the%20kingdom%20remains%20far%20below%20targets%20-%20just%20%2426%20billion%20in%202023%2C%20against%20an%20official%202030%20goal%20of%20%24100%20billion%20per%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPotential%20investors%20remain%20wary.%20Many%20are%20concerned%20about%20the%20scale%20and%20complexity%20of%20the%20projects%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20regulatory%20environment%20in%20Saudi%20Arabia.%20The%20International%20Monetary%20Fund%20has%20urged%20greater%20transparency%20on%20project%20spending.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741686360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-07%2Fonuopvvc_saudi-arabia-mirror-city-afp_625x300_27_July_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fsaudi-arabia-neom-the-line-50-billion-spent-what-went-wrong-at-saudi-arabias-sci-fi-desert-paradise-7898670%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Private%20yachts%20were%20moored%20nearby%2C%20and%20some%20of%20the%20biggest%20celebrities%20were%20in%20attendance%20as%20Saudi%20Arabia%20partially%20opened%20Neom%2C%20its%20ambitious%20%24500%20billion%20mega-city%20in%20the%20desert.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fsaudi-arabia-neom-the-line-50-billion-spent-what-went-wrong-at-saudi-arabias-sci-fi-desert-paradise-7898670%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20How%20China%20Is%20Increasing%20Surveillance%20Around%20India's%20Borders%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20recent%20statement%2C%20Chinese%20Foreign%20Minister%20Wang%20Yi%20asserted%20that%20India%20and%20China%20should%20%E2%80%9Csupport%20each%20other%20rather%20than%20undermine%20each%20other%20or%20undercut%20each%20other%26quot%3B%2C%20and%20that%20they%20%E2%80%9Cshould%20work%20with%20each%20other%20rather%20than%20guard%20against%20each%20other%E2%80%9D.%20On%20face%20value%2C%20the%20statement%20appears%20to%20indicate%20the%20positive%20momentum%20that%20India-China%20relations%20have%20witnessed%20since%20October%202024.%20After%20a%20gap%20of%20more%20than%20four%20years%20since%20the%20violent%202020%20Galwan%20Clashes%2C%20New%20Delhi%20and%20Beijing%20have%20started%20to%20discuss%20ways%20to%20proceed%20ahead%20with%20border%20patrolling%20and%20disengagement.%20With%20this%2C%20China%20has%20also%20continued%20to%20reiterate%20that%20the%20border%20issue%20should%20not%20be%20the%20central%20point%20to%20base%20the%20direction%20of%20the%20bilateral%20relations.%20Even%20though%20Beijing%20calls%20for%20%E2%80%9Ctrust%E2%80%9D%20and%20not%20guarding%20%E2%80%9Cagainst%20each%20other%E2%80%9D%2C%20it%20has%20continued%20to%20undertake%20surveillance%2C%20reconnaissance%20and%20monitoring%20exercises.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChinese%20efforts%20to%20gain%20influence%20and%20access%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20South%20Asian%20region%2C%20have%20grown%20consistently%20over%20the%20last%20few%20years.%20The%20Belt%20and%20Road%20Initiative%20(BRI)%2C%20which%20was%20launched%20in%202013%2C%20has%20helped%20Beijing%20gain%20a%20strong%20foothold%20in%20the%20region%20as%20it%20has%20used%20its%20economic%20prowess%20in%20the%20form%20of%20loans%20and%20aid%20to%20gain%20leverage.%20A%20number%20of%20South%20Asian%20countries%20are%20facing%20major%20debt%20challenges%20as%20a%20result%20of%20that.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ESri%20Lanka%20And%20Maldives%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20casualty%20was%20the%20leasing%20of%20the%20Hambantota%20Port%20by%20Sri%20Lanka%20to%20China%20in%202017%20for%20a%20period%20of%2099%20years.%20This%20has%20intensified%20New%20Delhi's%20security%20woes.%20China%20has%20also%20used%20its%20economic%20clout%20over%20Sri%20Lanka%20to%20let%20its%20spy%20ships%20and%20vessels%20dock%20there%20under%20the%20garb%20of%20research.%20These%20vehicles%20have%20consistently%20added%20to%20the%20Indian%20Navy's%20security%20challenges%2C%20as%20they%20can%20gather%20confidential%20data%20on%20movement%20and%20preparedness.%20In%202017%2C%20the%20Gwadar%20Port's%20day-to-day%20operations%20were%20also%20handed%20over%20to%20a%20Chinese%20state-run%20company%20for%2040%20years.%20China%20has%20also%20sent%20a%20number%20of%20submarines%20to%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENew%20Delhi%20faces%20a%20similar%20challenge%20from%20the%20Maldives%20as%20well.%20The%20strong%20tilt%20of%20Male%20towards%20Beijing%20under%20the%20Muizzu%20government%20is%20a%20cause%20of%20concern%20for%20India.%20Chinese%20ships%20have%20continued%20to%20dock%20in%20Male.%20Recent%20talks%20between%20China%20and%20Maldives%20also%20involved%20discussions%20about%20installing%20fish%20aggregating%20devices%20(FADs)%20in%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%20Region.%20In%20early%202024%2C%20%3Cem%3EXiang%20Yang%20Hong%2003%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20which%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20advanced%20research%20vessels%20in%20China%2C%20also%20visited%20Maldives.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20during%20a%202015%20visit%20to%20Mauritius%20that%20the%20Indian%20Prime%20Minister%20had%20envisioned%20the%20idea%20of%20Security%20and%20Growth%20for%20all%20in%20the%20Region%20(SAGAR).%20Years%20later%2C%20as%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20visits%20the%20island%20nation%20on%20March%2011-12%2C%20New%20Delhi%20is%20set%20to%20conclude%20MoUs%20that%20will%20help%20India%20in%20sharing%20white-shipping%20information%20and%20counter%20growing%20Chinese%20inroads.%20India%20has%20also%20been%20working%20towards%20strengthening%20its%20Lakshadweep%20Islands%20and%20has%20established%20the%3Cem%3E%20INS%20Jatayu%20base%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20on%20Minicoy%2C%20the%20southernmost%20archipelago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20LPAR%20In%20Yunnan%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20oceans%2C%20China%2C%20as%20per%20reports%2C%20also%20recently%20deployed%20a%20Large%20Phased%20Array%20Radar%20(LPAR)%20in%20Yunnan%20province%20and%20near%20the%20Myanmar%20border%2C%20which%20has%20a%20monitoring%20range%20of%205%2C000%20kilometres.%20This%20provides%20Beijing%20with%20access%20to%20a%20large%20tract%20of%20Indian%20land%2C%20which%20will%20help%20it%20keep%20tabs%20on%20missile%20and%20other%20air%20force%20movements.%20It%20is%20believed%20that%20this%20radar%20has%20the%20capacity%20to%20detect%20missile%20tests%20conducted%20at%20Abdul%20Kalam%20Island%20off%20the%20coast%20of%20Odisha.%20The%20island%20is%20used%20primarily%20for%20the%20launch%20of%20Agni%20V%2C%20an%20intercontinental%20missile%2C%20and%20of%20the%20K4%20submarine-launched%20missiles.%20Both%20these%20things%20compromise%20India's%20security%20preparedness%20as%20they%20help%20Beijing%20monitor%20every%20possible%20move%20undertaken%20by%20New%20Delhi.%20India%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20has%20been%20in%20talks%20with%20Moscow%20to%20receive%20the%20Voronezh%20radar%20system%20with%20a%20range%20of%208%2C000%20kilometres%2C%20a%20step%20that%20will%20enhance%20India's%20security%20apparatus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20not%20only%20land%20and%20sea%3B%20the%20Chinese%20space%20reconnaissance%20system%20is%20also%20quite%20sophisticated.%20Beijing%20had%20started%20this%20programme%20in%202006%20and%20has%20launched%20more%20than%20140%20Yaogan%20satellites%20so%20far.%20Yaogan%20can%20be%20literally%20translated%20as%20%E2%80%98remote%20sensing'.%20This%20coupled%20with%20its%20other%20satellite%20systems%2C%20like%20Gaofen%20and%20Shiyan%2C%20provides%20China%20with%20the%20capability%20to%20track%20even%20car-sized%20objects%20in%20the%20Indian%20and%20Pacific%20Oceans.%20As%20per%20reports%2C%20Beijing%20has%20a%20total%20of%20245%20operational%20reconnaissance%20satellites%2C%20while%20New%20Delhi%20has%20just%2026.%20The%20Chinese%20satellites%20also%20enjoy%20better%20range%2C%20resolution%20and%20all-weather%20capabilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ECaution%20Is%20Key%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20this%20backdrop%2C%20New%20Delhi%20has%20every%20reason%20to%20be%20on%20guard%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20moving%20ahead%20with%20any%20kind%20of%20normalisation%20with%20Beijing.%20The%20defence%20budget%20for%20China%20for%20fiscal%20year%202025%20has%20been%20set%20at%20%24246%20billion%2C%20while%20India's%20defence%20budget%20is%20at%20around%20%2482%20billion.%20China%20will%20be%20spending%20more%20than%20three%20times%20that%20of%20India%20in%20the%20next%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrue%2C%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20diplomatic%20channels%2C%20China%20has%20consistently%20argued%20that%20there%20is%20a%20need%20to%20push%20for%20building%20economic%20relations%20and%20reestablish%20people-to-people%20connections%20and%20direct%20flights%20between%20the%20two%20countries.%20India%20has%20been%20quite%20consistent%20in%20its%20argument%3A%20of%20keeping%20bilateral%20talks%20focused%20on%20the%20resolution%20of%20the%20border%20issue.%20Even%20so%2C%20it%20is%20quite%20obvious%20that%20China%20is%20fully%20cognisant%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20security%20is%20crucial%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20India-China%20relations%20and%20has%20been%20working%20towards%20building%20its%20security%20infrastructure.%20These%20developments%20should%20be%20taken%20into%20consideration%20when%20New%20Delhi%20answers%20Beijing's%20calls%20for%20a%20rethink%20on%20bilateral%20ties.%20This%20also%20raises%20the%20question%2C%20can%20India-China%20relations%20ever%20be%20based%20on%20mutual%20trust%20and%20respect%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(The%20author%20is%20a%20Professor%20at%20OP%20Jindal%20Global%20University)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741686300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-01%2F7rtk0vlg_india-china_625x300_13_January_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fwhy-china-is-increasing-surveillance-around-indias-borders-7898734%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22China%20is%20cognisant%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20security%20is%20crucial%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20India-China%20relations%20and%20has%20thus%20been%20building%20its%20security%20infrastructure.%20These%20developments%20should%20be%20considered%20when%20India%20answers%20Beijing's%20calls%20for%20a%20rethink%20on%20ties.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fwhy-china-is-increasing-surveillance-around-indias-borders-7898734%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20In%20Bihar%2C%20What%20Was%20Once%20Unthinkable%20Has%20Become%20The%20New%20Normal%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOn%20a%20computer%20screen%20at%20the%20Asian%20Development%20Research%20Institute%20(ADRI)%20in%20Patna%2C%20Dr%20Sanchita%20Mahapatra%2C%20who%20heads%20the%20centre%20for%20health%20policy%20division%2C%20point%20out%20a%20graph%2C%20displaying%20an%20innovative%20development%20index%20known%20as%20night%20time%20light%20(NTL)%20radiance%2C%20to%20trace%20the%20trajectory%20of%20Bihar's%20growth.%20The%20NTL%20radiance%20indicates%20the%20density%20of%20illumination%20in%20a%20given%20area%20at%20night%20time.%20Invariably%2C%20developed%20areas%20have%20a%20lot%20greater%20density%20of%20illumination%20as%20compared%20to%20underdeveloped%20regions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20that's%20a%20new%20way%20to%20map%20economic%20growth%2C%20Bihar%20seems%20to%20be%20growing%20at%20a%20fast%20pace.%20The%20decadal%20assessment%20shows%20that%20NTL%20radiance%20in%20the%20state%20has%20grown%20many%20times%20over%20as%20compared%20to%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20country.%20More%20than%20a%20decade%20back%2C%20the%20NTL%20radiance%20index%20showed%20Bihar%20as%20literally%20an%20area%20of%20darkness.%20But%20things%20are%20fast%20improving.%20The%20most%20illuminated%20city%20centres%20on%20the%20screen%20are%20identified%20as%20Patna%2C%20Jehanabad%2C%20Vaishali%20and%20Siwan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMahapatra%20has%20been%20exploring%20any%20correlation%20between%20the%20areas%20with%20increased%20NTL%20radiance%20and%20better%20health%20facilities.%20For%20the%20past%20many%20years%2C%20her%20team%20has%20been%20struggling%20to%20get%20the%20exact%20feedback%20on%20outbreak%20of%20infectious%20diseases%20from%20the%20ground.%20Years%20of%20persistent%20training%20and%20persuasion%20of%20the%20ground%20staff%20eventually%20yielded%20positive%20results.%20Now%20there%20is%20a%20mechanism%20in%20place%20to%20get%20real-time%20data%20on%20the%20spread%20of%20infectious%20diseases.%20A%20timely%20alert%20can%20avert%20a%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20Bihar%20ranks%20among%20the%20top%20five%20states%20on%20the%20index%20of%20real-time%20reporting%20of%20the%20diseases.%20There%20is%20no%20doubt%20that%20the%20health%20facilities%20are%20still%20lagging%20far%20behind%20when%20compared%20with%20other%2C%20developed%20regions%20of%20the%20country.%20Yet%20Bihar%20has%20been%20moving%20fast%20to%20fill%20up%20the%20deficit%20inherited%20by%20the%20legacy%20of%20past%20indiscretions%20in%20governance.%20Patna%20promises%20to%20build%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20hospitals%20in%20the%20world%20under%20the%20aegis%20of%20the%20prestigious%20Patna%20Medical%20college%20Hospital%20(PMCH)%20which%20celebrated%20its%20centenary%20on%20February%2026.%20President%20Droupadi%20Murmu%20inaugurated%20it%20and%20lauded%20the%20contribution%20of%20the%20PMCH%20and%20its%20luminaries%20in%20strengthening%20India's%20healthcare%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20the%20government%20initiatives%20like%20the%20setting%20up%20of%20new%20medical%20colleges%2C%20including%20two%20AIIMS%2C%20the%20striking%20feature%20of%20healthcare%20in%20the%20state%20today%20is%20a%20surfeit%20of%20private%20investment.%20Much%20like%20the%20fast%20pace%20of%20illumination%20in%20Bihar%2C%20several%20pockets%20of%20bright%20spots%20have%20emerged%20where%20private%20medical%20facilities%20have%20come%20up%20in%20numbers.%20In%20addition%20to%20Patna%2C%20Muzaffarpur%20has%20always%20been%20a%20hub%20of%20good%20doctors.%20Of%20late%2C%20thousands%20of%20private%20hospitals%20and%20health%20facilities%20have%20been%20set%20up%20to%20cater%20to%20people%20in%20the%20state%20which%20has%20the%20highest%20population%20density%20in%20the%20country.%20And%20most%20of%20these%20hospitals%20are%20linked%20to%20the%20Ayushman%20Bharat-Pradhan%20Mantri%20Jan%20Arogya%20Yojana%20(ABPMJAY)%20to%20assist%20the%20most%20vulnerable%20sections%20of%20the%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeneficiaries%20of%20the%20Ayushman%20Bharat%20Yojana%20are%20getting%20treatment%20for%20ailments%20ranging%20from%20heart%20disease%20to%20cancer%20in%20hospitals%20all%20over%20the%20state%20free%20of%20cost.%20In%20some%20cases%20where%20specialist%20treatment%20is%20required%2C%20patients%20are%20treated%20at%20super-speciality%20centres%20at%20Patna%20or%20referred%20to%20specialised%20centres%20in%20Delhi%20or%20Mumbai.%20What%20is%20particularly%20encouraging%20is%20the%20growth%20of%20specialised%20medical%20health%20care%20centres%20which%20were%20nonexistent%20till%20a%20decade%20ago.%20The%20improved%20health%20facilities%20in%20the%20state%20are%20as%20much%20a%20sign%20of%20changing%20Bihar%20as%20an%20increased%20NTL%20radiance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20late%20there%20has%20been%20no%20outbreak%20of%20diseases%20which%20used%20to%20be%20endemic%20in%20Bihar.%20The%20real-time%20reporting%20of%20diseases%20like%20Kala-Azar%2C%20flu%20or%20encephalitis%20has%20enabled%20the%20health%20machinery%20to%20prevent%20the%20snowballing%20of%20any%20outbreak%20into%20a%20crisis.%20This%20is%20in%20stark%20contrast%20to%20the%20time%20when%20people%20had%20no%20option%20but%20to%20suffer%20in%20silence.%20Bihar%20has%20been%20showing%20a%20consistent%20improvement%20in%20the%20health%20index.%20This%20was%20especially%20evident%20when%20Bihar%20handled%20the%20Covid-19%20pandemic%20as%20deftly%20as%20developed%20regions%20of%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20those%20who%20lived%20in%20Bihar%20in%20the%20early%20nineties%2C%20the%20discernible%20changes%20in%20Bihar%20are%20nothing%20short%20of%20a%20silent%20revolution.%20When%20I%20worked%20as%20a%20journalist%20based%20in%20Patna%20in%201991%2C%20the%20state%20was%20plagued%20by%20acute%20power%20shortages%2C%20poor%20connectivity%20due%20to%20bad%20roads%20and%20a%20pathetic%20healthcare%20system.%20Even%20in%20a%20city%20like%20Patna%2C%20the%20rule%20of%20law%20was%20practically%20replaced%20by%20the%20%26quot%3Bsurvival%20of%20the%20fittest%26quot%3B%2C%20leading%20to%20the%20migration%20of%20doctors%2C%20engineers%20and%20entrepreneurs%20out%20of%20the%20state.%20In%20rural%20parts%2C%20the%20situation%20was%20even%20worse.%20The%20decade%20of%20the%20nineties%20was%20marked%20by%20massacres%20on%20caste%20lines%2C%20taking%20social%20discord%20to%20an%20extreme%20that%20turned%20many%20villages%20inhospitable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20scary%20past%20seems%20so%20distant%20when%20one%20drives%20through%20Patna%20and%20other%20parts%20of%20Bihar%20today.%20Roads%20are%20far%20better%2C%20the%20traffic%20is%20flowing%20smoothly%20and%20police%20officers%20keeping%20a%20watch%20are%20mostly%20women.%20In%20the%20evening%2C%20people%20including%20young%20couples%20throng%20a%20newly%20constructed%20boulevard%20across%20the%20Ganga%2C%20better%20known%20as%20%26quot%3BMarine%20Drive%26quot%3B.%20These%20scenes%20were%20outright%20inconceivable%20in%20the%20nineties%20when%20an%20evening%20stroll%20in%20the%20city%20was%20considered%20to%20be%20a%20risky%20proposition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20no%20doubt%20that%20Bihar%20needs%20to%20grow%20at%20a%20much%20faster%20pace%20to%20catch%20up%20with%20the%20developed%20parts%20of%20the%20country.%20During%20that%20wasted%20decade%2C%20its%20growth%20curve%20had%20not%20only%20stagnated%20but%20had%20been%20pushed%20back.%20Despondency%20was%20in%20the%20air%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20retrogressive%20mindset.%20The%20state%20