2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ETiesto%20saved%20%2428%20million%20over%20six%20years%20through%20illegal%20offshore%20tax%20shelters%2C%20court%20documents%20show.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EProsecutors%20now%20want%20the%20tax%20attorney%20who%20masterminded%20the%20scheme%20to%20personally%20pay%20most%20of%20it%20back.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20tax%20attorney%20counters%20that%20Tiesto%20should%20be%20responsible%20for%20his%20own%20back%20taxes.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Thursday%2C%20DJ%20Tiesto%2C%20who%20earns%20millions%20a%20year%20spinning%20electronic%20dance%20music%20at%20venues%20worldwide%2C%20will%20be%20midway%20into%20a%20three-show%20swing%20through%20Vegas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20same%20day%2C%20his%20former%20tax%20attorney%20will%20be%20in%20a%20federal%20courtroom%20in%20White%20Plains%2C%20New%20York%20%E2%80%94%20trying%20to%20not%20get%20stuck%20with%20the%20bill%20for%20the%20Dutch%20DJ's%20back%20taxes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFederal%20prosecutors%20say%20Frank%20Butselaar%20%E2%80%94%20known%20in%20the%20Dutch%20media%20as%20Holland's%20%26quot%3Btax%20attorney%20to%20the%20stars%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20set%20up%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdj-tiestos-tax-attorney-sentenced-hid-income-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ean%20illegal%20web%20of%20offshore%20shelters%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20saved%20Tiesto%20%2428%20million%20in%20US%20taxes%20over%20six%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EProsecutors%20have%20not%20accused%20Tiesto%20of%20wrongdoing%20and%20have%20said%20he%20was%20unaware%20that%20the%20offshore%20structures%20were%20illegal.%20Court%20documents%20show%20the%20IRS%20capped%20Tiesto's%20own%20obligation%20at%20%249%2C467%2C085%2C%20an%20amount%20that%20federal%20prosecutors%20say%20the%20DJ%20has%20paid%20%26quot%3Bvoluntarily.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20though%2C%20prosecutors%20are%20taking%20Butselaar%20back%20to%20court%20to%20ask%20a%20judge%20to%20order%20restitution%20for%20the%20balance%20%E2%80%94%20some%20%2419%20million%20in%20Tiesto's%20unpaid%20taxes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20filing%20from%20Monday%2C%20March%203%2C%20prosecutors%20said%20that%20if%20Butselaar%20plays%20nice%20and%20agrees%20to%20pay%20without%20a%20fight%2C%20they'll%20cut%20him%20a%20break%20and%20limit%20their%20request%20for%20restitution%20to%20%2415.5%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EButselaar's%20lawyer%20plans%20to%20counter%20that%20his%20client%20is%20broke%2C%20that%20any%20restitution%20amount%20should%20be%20determined%20via%20an%20exhaustive%20hearing%2C%20and%20that%20back%20taxes%20should%20be%20the%20burden%20of%20the%20taxpayer%20%E2%80%94%20meaning%20Tiesto.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMr.%20Butselaar%20was%20paid%20an%20hourly%20rate%20to%20help%20his%20clients%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20lawyer%2C%20Kerry%20Lawrence%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BIf%20anyone%20is%20held%20liable%20to%20pay%20taxes%20on%20the%20millions%20of%20dollars%20in%20income%20it%20should%20be%20the%20artists%20who%20earned%20it%2C%20not%20Mr.%20Butselaar.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReps%20for%20Tiesto%20%E2%80%94%20given%20name%20Tijs%20Verwest%20%E2%80%94%20declined%20requests%20for%20an%20on-the-record%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b24d9500-d678-4a97-840a-682b6482a6c7%5C%22%3E%2419%20million%20is%20'a%20lot'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhite-collar%20defense%20lawyers%20and%20tax%20law%20experts%20told%20Business%20Insider%20they%20had%20never%20heard%20of%20a%20tax%20attorney%20or%20accountant%20being%20ordered%20to%20pay%20such%20a%20high%20amount%20of%20their%20client's%20back%20taxes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20last%20week's%20filing%2C%20Butselaar's%20prosecutors%20offered%20US%20District%20Judge%20Cathy%20Seibel%20three%20examples.%20The%20highest%20restitution%20cited%20was%20%242%20million%2C%20the%20amount%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.justice.gov%2Fusao-ndms%2Fpr%2Ftax-preparer-sentenced-18-months-serve-and-196-million-restitution%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20federal%20judge%20in%20Mississippi%3C%2Fa%3E%20ordered%20a%20tax%20preparer%20to%20pay%20the%20IRS%20in%20late%20January.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20federal%20law%20holds%20tax%20preparers%20liable%20if%20it's%20proven%20that%20they%20knowingly%20hid%20their%20clients'%20income%2C%20said%20John%20Moscow%2C%20a%20longtime%20financial%20crimes%20prosecutor%20for%20the%20Manhattan%20District%20Attorney's%20Office.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNineteen%20million%20%E2%80%94%20that's%20a%20lot%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Moscow%2C%20now%20senior%20counsel%20at%20Lewis%20Baach%20Kaufmann%20Middlemiss%20in%20New%20York.%20%26quot%3BBut%20it%20seems%20appropriate%20for%20the%20federal%20government%20to%20tell%20a%20tax%20preparer%2C%20'You%20knew%20it%20was%20a%20crime%3B%20pay%20it%20back%20to%20us.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20offshore%20structures%20Butselaar%20created%20for%20Tiesto%20hid%20tens%20of%20millions%20in%20income%20earned%20from%20overseas%20performances%20between%202012%20to%202017%2C%20and%20caused%20a%20total%20IRS%20tax%20loss%20of%20%2428%2C020%2C413%20%E2%80%94%20money%20prosecutors%20say%20the%20DJ%20should%20have%20paid%20after%20qualifying%20as%20a%20US%20tax%20resident%20in%20each%20of%20those%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EButselaar%20has%20also%20admitted%20saving%20fellow%20Dutch%20DJ%20Afrojack%20%24700%2C000%20on%20his%202013%20taxes%20through%20an%20identical%20offshore%20shelter%20scheme.%20As%20with%20Tiesto%2C%20Afrojack%20%E2%80%94%20given%20name%20Nick%20van%20de%20Wall%20%E2%80%94%20has%20not%20been%20implicated%20in%20wrongdoing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Afrojack's%20%24700%2C000%20tax%20savings%20are%20added%20in%2C%20and%20Tiesto's%20%249%20million%20payment%20is%20subtracted%2C%20%26quot%3Bthe%20total%20outstanding%20tax%20loss%20to%20the%20IRS%20from%20Butselaar's%20actions%20is%20%2419%2C250%2C845%2C%26quot%3B%20prosecutors%20wrote%20last%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BButselaar's%20efforts%20to%20escape%20his%20restitution%20obligations%20are%20unpersuasive%2C%20unsupported%20by%20law%2C%20and%20contrary%20to%20the%20plea%20agreement%20that%20both%20he%20and%20his%20lawyers%20signed%2C%26quot%3B%20prosecutors%20wrote%20in%20their%20filing%20to%20the%20judge%20last%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EProsecutors%20also%20wrote%20that%20they%20hope%20Seibel%20will%20order%20Butselaar%20to%20pay%20up%20immediately%20before%20they%20leave%20the%20courtroom.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b48ae586-1e4a-497d-a5a0-1620427234b3%5C%22%3EThe%20IRS%20lost%20at%20least%20%2425%20million%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EButselaar%2C%2065%2C%20is%20in%20a%20Westchester%20County%2C%20New%20York%2C%20jail%2C%20serving%20the%20final%20six%20months%20of%20a%2030-month%20federal%20sentence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20November%20tax-fraud%20plea%2C%20he%20admitted%20that%20the%20offshore%20shelters%20he%20devised%20for%20the%20Dutch%20DJs%20and%20fashion%20models%20on%20his%20client%20list%20had%20cost%20the%20IRS%20at%20least%20%2425%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EProsecutors%20described%20the%20scheme%20this%20way%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EButselar%20set%20up%20a%20web%20of%20companies%20to%20segregate%20his%20clients'%20US-generated%20income%20from%20their%20overseas%20income.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20overseas%20companies%2C%20typically%20set%20up%20in%20Cyprus%20and%20Guernsey%2C%20were%20controlled%20by%20trusts%20with%20straw%20beneficiaries%2C%20and%20the%20non-US%20income%20that%20flowed%20into%20them%20would%20not%20be%20reported%20to%20the%20IRS.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EButselaar's%20clients%20would%20report%20only%20their%20US-generated%20income%20on%20their%20tax%20returns%2C%20even%20though%2C%20as%20US%20resident%20taxpayers%2C%20they%20needed%20to%20report%20all%20of%20their%20income%20worldwide.%20Overseas%20citizens%20qualify%20for%20US%20tax-residency%20status%20%E2%80%94%20and%20must%2C%20therefore%2C%20pay%20US%20taxes%20on%20the%20entirety%20of%20their%20income%20%E2%80%94%20if%20they%20live%20in%20the%20states%20for%20183%20or%20more%20days%20in%20a%20single%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20total%2C%20Butselaar%20hid%20between%20%2470%20million%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.justice.gov%2Fusao-sdny%2Fpr%2Finternational-tax-advisor-arrested-helping-conceal-over-100-million-income-high-net%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eand%20%24100%20million%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20reportable%20overseas%20income%20from%20the%20IRS%2C%20prosecutors%20alleged.%20The%20scheme%20was%20discovered%20in%20March%202018%20by%20Dutch%20authorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELearning%20of%20the%20criminal%20investigation%2C%20Tiesto%20hired%20a%20prominent%20international%20law%20firm%2C%20Kramer%20Levin%20Naftalis%20%26amp%3B%20Frankel%2C%20to%20review%20his%20offshore%20setup.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20Dutch%20criminal%20investigation%20and%20Kramer%20Levin's%20analysis%2C%20Verwest%20eventually%20fired%20Butselaar%2C%26quot%3B%20prosecutors%20wrote%20in%20February%2C%20using%20Tiesto's%20given%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e0511c6a-52f9-44e6-a420-61a1343d65d1%5C%22%3EA%20modest%20home%20in%20Italy%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Thursday%2C%20Butselaar's%20lawyer%20plans%20to%20argue%20that%20his%20client%20has%20limited%20financial%20means%20and%20that%20the%20judge%20has%20the%20discretion%20to%20order%20no%20restitution%20at%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMr.%20Butselaar's%20sole%20asset%20is%20a%20modest%20home%20in%20Italy%20that%20he%20and%20his%20wife%20are%20selling%20to%20repay%20a%20loan%20extended%20by%20a%20friend%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20defense%20of%20this%20case%2C%26quot%3B%20Lawrence%20wrote%20the%20judge%2C%20referring%20to%20his%20client's%20holiday%20villa%20in%20the%20medieval%20town%20of%20Valfabbrica%2C%20near%20Perugia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnder%20a%20November%20plea%20deal%2C%20Butselaar%20pleaded%20guilty%20to%20a%20single%20tax%20fraud%20count%2C%20telling%20the%20judge%20he%20filed%20a%20false%202013%20return%20for%20Afrojack.%20Lawrence%20now%20argues%20that%20any%20restitution%20should%20be%20limited%20to%20back%20taxes%20relating%20to%20that%20one%20count.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EProsecutors%20say%20Butselaar%20approached%20at%20least%20six%20other%20professionals%2C%20including%20American%20CPAs%20and%20tax%20lawyers%2C%20but%20they%20refused%20to%20participate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20professionals%20instead%20told%20the%20tax%20lawyer%20that%20the%20offshore%20income%20being%20accumulated%20outside%20the%20US%20by%20the%20two%20DJs%20needed%20to%20be%20reported%20to%20the%20IRS%2C%20prosecutors%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EProsecutors%20have%20not%20sought%20charges%20or%20restitution%20against%20Butselaar's%20unindicted%20co-conspirators%3A%20an%20entertainment%20management%20firm%20and%20two%20employees%20who%20did%20agree%20to%20sign%20years%20of%20fraudulent%20tax%20returns.%20Their%20names%20remain%20redacted%20in%20the%20court%20record.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fembed.documentcloud.org%2Fdocuments%2F25551054-us-v-butselaar-joint-restitution-filing-20250303pdf%2F%3Fembed%3D1%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600px%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiesto-saved-28m-through-illegal-offshore-accounts-2025-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741684261000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67cb191369253ccddf9897b9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiesto-saved-28m-through-illegal-offshore-accounts-2025-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22On%20Thursday%2C%20Tiesto's%20ex-tax%20attorney%2C%20now%20jailed%20on%20tax%20fraud%2C%20will%20fight%20having%20to%20pay%20as%20much%20as%20%2419M%20in%20the%20Dutch%