C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fimages%2Fic%2F1200x675%2Fp01tqv8z.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fprogrammes%2Fp0kxdzw0%233%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Russia%3A%20At%20the%20scene%20of%20drone%20attack%20on%20Moscow%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A26%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fprogrammes%2Fp0kxdzw0%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22NDTV%20Explains%20New%20Bill%20That%20Can%20Deny%20Foreigners%20Visas%20Over%20'National%20Security'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EForeigners%20can%20be%20denied%20visas%20on%20national%20security%20grounds%2C%20their%20movements%20can%20be%20restricted%2C%20and%20they%20can%20be%20penalised%20for%20violating%20rules%20governing%20their%20entry%20into%2C%20and%20exit%20from%2C%20India%2C%20according%20to%20a%20proposed%20law%20tabled%20in%20Parliament%20Tuesday%20by%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Immigration%20and%20Foreigners%20Bill%2C%202025%2C%20is%20meant%20to%20'modernise%20and%20consolidate'%20existing%20laws%20on%20this%20topic%2C%20and%20will%20also%20give%20the%20government%20the%20power%20to%20regulate%20admission%20of%20foreigners%20into%20universities%20and%20hospitals%2C%20as%20well%20as%20other%20educational%20and%20medical%20institutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20law%20will%20replace%20four%20that%20govern%20the%20entry%20of%20foreigners%20and%20includes%20the%20requirement%20for%20passports%20and%20visas.%20These%20are%20the%20Passport%20(Entry%20into%20India)%20Act%2C%201920%3B%20the%20Registration%20of%20Foreigners%20Act%2C%201939%3B%20the%20Foreigners%20Act%2C%201946%3B%20and%20the%20Immigration%20(Carriers'%20Liability)%20Act%2C%202000.%20The%20first%20three%20were%20passed%20by%20the%20British%20and%20the%20result%20of%20a%20post-World%20War%20scenario.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20has%20said%20the%20new%20law%20will%20also%20re-define%20the%20role%20and%20function%20of%20immigration%20officers%2C%20whose%20word%20on%20denial%20of%20visas%20over%20'threats%20to%20national%20security'%20will%20be%20binding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government's%20ability%20to%20deport%20foreigners%2C%20or%20offer%20exemption%2C%20will%20also%20be%20specified.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Immigration%20Law%20Details%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20immigration%20bill%2C%20sources%20told%20NDTV%2C%20is%20being%20enacted%20to%20avoid%20multiplicity%20and%20overlapping%20of%20laws%20on%20the%20same%2C%20or%20related%20subject%2C%20and%20to%20simplify%20the%20language.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20six%20chapters%20-%20with%20a%20total%20of%2035%20clauses%20-%20in%20this%20new%20text.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20other%20points%2C%20the%20new%20bill%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EDefines%20the%20role%20and%20function%20of%20an%20immigration%20officer%2C%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ERequirements%2C%20including%20passports%2C%20for%20the%20issue%20of%20visas%2C%20and%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ERegistration%20of%20foreigners.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20functions%20are%20currently%20handled%20by%20the%20Bureau%20of%20Immigration%2C%20which%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bprofessional%2C%20effective%2C%20and%20efficient%20immigration%20service%20to%20facilitate%20legitimate%20travellers%2C%20while%20ensuring%20national%20security%26quot%3B.%20Sources%20told%20NDTV%20the%20new%20law%20will%20give%20that%20agency%20more%20legal%20backing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20law%20will%20also%20regulate%20the%20conditions%20for%20universities%20and%20hospitals'%20offers%20of%20admittance%20to%20foreigners.%20Sources%20said%20this%20addition%20is%20necessary%20since%20there%20is%20no%20rule%2C%20at%20present%2C%20on%20this%20topic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EForeigners%20are%2C%20however%2C%20required%20to%20register%20with%20the%20Foreigners%20Regional%20Registration%20Office%2C%20in%20accordance%20with%20the%20Passport%20(Entry%20into%20India)%20Act%2C%20the%20Foreigners%20Act%2C%20and%20the%20Registration%20of%20Foreigners%20Act.%20The%20term%20'foreigners'%2C%20in%20this%20case%2C%20also%20refers%20to%20those%20of%20Indian%20origin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Home%20Ministry%2C%20those%20visiting%20India%20for%20more%20than%20180%20days%2C%20whether%20for%20medical%2C%20employment%2C%20education%2C%20or%20research%20purposes%2C%20must%20register%20themselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETourists%20are%20exempt%20providing%20they%20do%20not%20stay%20continuously%20for%20more%20than%20180%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EForeigners%20will%20continue%20to%20be%20required%20to%20carry%20proof%20of%20foreign%20status%20-%20i.e.%2C%20a%20passport%20or%20an%20equally%20applicable%20document%20-%20at%20all%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EForeigners%20As%20'National%20Security%20Threat'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20specific%20section%20in%20the%20new%20law%20states%20-%20%26quot%3B...%20no%20foreigner%20shall%20be%20allowed%20to%20enter%20into%2C%20or%20stay%20in%20India%2C%20if%20s%2Fhe%20is%20found%20inadmissible%20to%20do%20so%20on%20account%20of%20threat%20to%20national%20security%2C%20sovereignty%2C%20and%20integrity%20of%20India...%20or%20on%20such%20other%20grounds%20as%20the%20government%20may%20specify%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDenying%20entry%20is%20not%20a%20new%20topic.%20In%20fact%2C%20last%20month%20Indian-American%20politician%20Kshama%20Sawant%20was%20denied%20-%20not%20for%20the%20first%20time%20-%20a%20visa%20to%20visit%20her%20ailing%20mother%20in%20Bengaluru.%20She%20claimed%20she%20had%20been%20rejected%20thrice%20while%20her%20husband%2C%20Calvin%20Priest%2C%20was%20granted%20an%20emergency%20visa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20post%20on%20X%20she%20said%20it%20was%20because%20%26quot%3BI'm%20on%20(the%20Narendra)%20Modi%20government's%20'reject%20list'%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Sawant%20is%20a%20long-time%20vocal%20critic%20of%20the%20ruling%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%2C%20last%20year%2C%20the%20government%20refused%20entry%20to%20Nitasha%20Kaul%2C%20a%20British%20national.%20She%20was%20deported%2C%20she%20claimed%2C%20shortly%20after%20her%20arrival%20at%20the%20airport%20in%20Bengaluru.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDenial%20of%20entry%20to%20foreigners%20was%20not%20explicitly%20mentioned%20in%20earlier%20laws%2C%20but%20there%20was%20a%20notification%20issued%20by%20the%20Home%20Ministry%20in%20February%201948%2C%20called%20The%20Foreigners%20Order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20allowed%20the%20government%20to%20deny%20entry%20if%20s%2Fhe%20does%20not%20hold%20a%20valid%20visa%2C%20or%20is%20of%20%26quot%3Bunsound%20mind%26quot%3B%2C%20or%20suffers%20from%20a%20%26quot%3Bloathsome%20or%20infectious%20disease%26quot%3B%2C%20or%20%26quot%3Bsentenced%20in%20foreign%20country%20for%20an%20extradition%20offence%26quot%3B.%20Entry%20can%20also%20be%20refused%20%26quot%3Bunder%20an%20issued%20by%20a%20competent%20authority%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENDTV%20is%20now%20available%20on%20WhatsApp%20channels.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whatsapp.com%2Fchannel%2F0029Va4lixw7z4kcvZI9JM12%5C%22%3EClick%20on%20the%20link%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20get%20all%20the%20latest%20updates%20from%20NDTV%20on%20your%20chat.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741676580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2016-01%2Findia-visa-indian-visa_650x400_71452521502.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fndtv-explains-immigration-and-foreigners-bill-2025-explained-foreigners-can-be-denied-visa-on-national-security-grounds-amit-shah-7897652%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Foreigners%20can%20be%20denied%20visas%20on%20national%20security%20grounds%2C%20their%20movements%20can%20be%20restricted%2C%20and%20they%20can%20be%20penalised%20for%20violating%20rules%20governing%20entry%20into%2C%20and%20exit%20from%2C%20India%2C%20according%20to%20a%20proposed%20l