d%20by%20the%20Directorate%20of%20Revenue%20Intelligence%20(DRI)%20for%20allegedly%20smuggling%20gold%20bars%20worth%20Rs%2012%20crore%20from%20Dubai%20to%20Bengaluru.%20She%20allegedly%20used%20VIP%20airport%20privileges%2C%20meant%20for%20senior%20officials%2C%20to%20bypass%20security%20checks%20and%20facilitate%20her%20smuggling%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Rao%20allegedly%20used%20her%20father's%20name%20and%20position%20as%20the%20Managing%20Director%20of%20the%20Karnataka%20State%20Police%20Housing%20and%20Infrastructure%20Development%20Corporation%20to%20gain%20unauthorised%20access%20to%20restricted%20airport%20facilities.%20The%20Karnataka%20government%20has%20issued%20an%20order%20to%20investigate%20the%20circumstances%20under%20which%20protocol%20privileges%20were%20extended%20to%20Ranya%20Rao%20and%20whether%20her%20father%20had%20any%20involvement%20in%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20government%20has%20appointed%20Gaurav%20Gupta%2C%20IAS%2C%20Additional%20Chief%20Secretary%2C%20as%20the%20investigating%20officer.%20The%20investigation%20has%20been%20ordered%20to%20begin%20immediately%2C%20with%20a%20final%20report%20expected%20within%20one%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20gold%20smuggling%20case%20has%20triggered%20a%20political%20debate%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20with%20the%20ruling%20Congress%20and%20the%20opposition%20BJP%20accusing%20each%20other%20of%20wrongdoing.%20The%20BJP%20has%20alleged%20that%20the%20Congress%20played%20a%20role%20in%20shielding%20Ms%20Rao%20from%20scrutiny.%20The%20Congress%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20has%20accused%20the%20BJP%20of%20granting%20land%20to%20a%20company%20linked%20to%20the%20actress%20under%20questionable%20circumstances.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20Karnataka%20President%20BY%20Vijayendra%20took%20to%20social%20media%20to%20criticise%20the%20government%2C%20stating%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMedia%20reports%20about%20the%20involvement%20of%20a%20prominent%20minister%20in%20%40siddaramaiah's%20government%20in%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20gold%20heists%20in%20recent%20times%20come%20as%20no%20surprise%20-%20especially%20given%20this%20government's%20track%20record%20of%20churning%20out%20scandals%20in%20increasingly%20'innovative'%20ways!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20alleged%20that%20the%20misuse%20of%20government%20protocols%20to%20smuggle%20gold%20worth%20over%20Rs%2012%20crore%20could%20not%20have%20happened%20without%20high-level%20political%20backing.%20Mr%20Vijayendra%20warned%20that%20any%20attempt%20to%20shield%20those%20responsible%20would%20backfire%2C%20particularly%20with%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%20stepping%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EState%20Home%20Minister%20G%20Parameshwara%20maintained%20that%20the%20investigation%20was%20ongoing%20and%20that%20the%20government%20would%20not%20intervene%20until%20the%20findings%20were%20clear.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUntil%20the%20investigation%20concludes%2C%20we%20cannot%20say%20anything.%20Neither%20I%20nor%20the%20government%20can%20offer%20any%20such%20feedback%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKarnataka%20minister%20MB%20Patil%20countered%20the%20BJP's%20allegations%20by%20pointing%20out%20that%20during%20the%20previous%20BJP-led%20administration%2C%2012%20acres%20of%20land%20had%20been%20allotted%20to%20a%20company%20linked%20to%20Ranya%20Rao.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741674600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fhot3ud38_ranya-rao-gold-smuggling-case_625x300_05_March_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Franya-rao-took-advantage-of-vip-protocol-karnataka-orders-new-probe-7897372%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Karnataka%20government%20has%20launched%20an%20inquiry%20into%20the%20alleged%20misuse%20of%20VIP%20airport%20protocol%20privileges%20by%20actress%20Ranya%20Rao%2C%20who%20was%20recently%20arrested%20in%20connection%20with%20a%20gold%20smuggling%20case.%22%2C%22