22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EManipur%E2%80%99s%20diverse%20landscape%20is%20home%20to%20a%20variety%20of%20flowers%2C%20from%20the%20striking%20gomphrena%20to%20the%20elegant%20rose.%20These%20blooms%20not%20only%20enhance%20the%20region%E2%80%99s%20beauty%20but%20also%20support%20local%20livelihoods.%20One%20such%20entrepreneur%20is%2027-year-old%20Khundrakpam%20Rani%20from%20Tera%20Lukram%20Leirak%20in%20Imphal%20West%20district%2C%20who%20has%20turned%20her%20passion%20for%20flowers%20into%20a%20thriving%20venture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGrowing%20up%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F359452%2Fflower-gardening-business-portulaca-farming-by-kerala-alappuzha-engineer-making-lakhs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esurrounded%20by%20flowers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Rani%20developed%20a%20deep%20appreciation%20for%20them%2C%20especially%20the%20ones%20in%20her%20family%E2%80%99s%20garden.%20%E2%80%9C%20%E2%80%9CI%20always%20loved%20flowers.%20We%20had%20so%20many%20beautiful%20blooms%20in%20our%20garden.%20The%20sight%20of%20fresh%20flowers%20would%20fill%20me%20with%20joy%2C%20but%20I%20hated%20seeing%20them%20wilt%20after%20being%20plucked%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Rani%2C%20with%20a%20nostalgic%20smile.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20childhood%20fascination%20with%20flowers%2C%20combined%20with%20her%20mother%E2%80%99s%20shared%20love%20for%20gardening%2C%20sowed%20the%20seeds%20of%20her%20business.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%222400846096%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERani%E2%80%99s%20mother%2C%20Khundrakpam%20Nandarani%2C%20recalls%20how%2C%20together%2C%20they%20grew%20a%20variety%20of%20flowers%20like%20gomphrena%2C%20dahlias%2C%20roses%2C%20celosias%2C%20helichrysum%2C%20chrysanthemums%2C%20and%20portulacas%20in%20their%20garden.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20spent%20hours%20tending%20to%20the%20flowers%2C%20and%20I%20would%20watch%20my%20daughter%20marvel%20at%20their%20beauty%2C%E2%80%9D%20Nandarani%20shares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20no%20surprise%20that%20Rani%20pursued%20her%20master%E2%80%99s%20in%20botany%20from%20Manipur%20University.%20Her%20love%20for%20flowers%20naturally%20extended%20into%20a%20desire%20to%20learn%20more%20about%20plant%20life.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20mother%E2%80%99s%20love%20for%20flowers%20also%20influenced%20me.%20She%20would%20teach%20me%20about%20the%20different%20flowers%2C%20and%20that%20inspired%20me%20to%20explore%20the%20world%20of%20plants%20on%20a%20greater%20level%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Why%20not%20use%20the%20wildflowers%3F%E2%80%99%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20her%20studies%2C%20specifically%20during%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%2C%20the%20young%20entrepreneur%20stumbled%20upon%20an%20idea%20that%20would%20mould%20her%20future.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229253875046%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20lockdowns%20in%20place%20and%20nothing%20much%20to%20do%2C%20she%20spent%20most%20of%20her%20time%20scrolling%20through%20social%20media.%20She%20noticed%20many%20people%20turning%20their%20passions%20into%20successful%20ventures%2C%20which%20inspired%20her%20to%20take%20the%20plunge.%20%E2%80%9CI%20thought%20to%20myself%2C%20why%20not%20use%20the%20wildflowers%20I%20love%20so%20much%20to%20create%20something%20beautiful%20and%20enduring%3F%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20Thus%2C%20%E2%80%98Dry%20Bloom%E2%80%99%20was%20born%20in%20December%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22w