A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2Fgardening-6-1741097520-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2Fgardening-6-1741097520-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-411592%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EBougainvilleas%20(L)%20and%20%3Cem%3EMonstera%20deliciosa%3C%2Fem%3E%20(R)%20or%20the%20Swiss%20cheese%20plant%20flaunt%20their%20beauty%20at%20Veena%E2%80%99s%20residence%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20intriguing%20to%20watch%20it%20bloom%20in%20her%20home%20today.%20%E2%80%9CI%20just%20needed%20to%20find%20the%20right%20place%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%20In%20winter%2C%20she%E2%80%99s%20learnt%20to%20allow%20the%20Boston%20fern%20to%20enjoy%20a%20window%20seat.%20%E2%80%9CAs%20the%20weather%20changes%20around%20May%2C%20and%20the%20hot%20winds%20start%20blowing%20across%20North%20India%2C%20I%20move%20these%20plants%20to%20a%20shaded%20area.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPlant%20your%20air%20purifier%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202024%20(until%20December%2027)%2C%20Delhi%20witnessed%20155%20days%20of%20%E2%80%98poor%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%98very%20poor%E2%80%99%2C%20or%20%E2%80%98severe%E2%80%99%20air%20quality%2C%20that%20is%2C%20with%20an%20air%20quality%20index%20(AQI)%20of%20200%20or%20more.%20But%20Veena%20and%20her%20husband%20weren%E2%80%99t%20perturbed.%20The%20%E2%80%98purifier%E2%80%99%20plants%20came%20to%20the%20rescue%2C%20Veena%20says%2C%20motioning%20to%20the%20snake%20plant%20(Dracaena%20trifasciata)%2C%20also%20called%20%E2%80%98mother-in-law%E2%80%99s%20tongue%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20is%20touted%20as%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F220484%2Fbengaluru-engineering-student-innovation-filter-soot-air-pollution-environment-india-say143%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5